==> 943.reply.3 <==
From: paul murrell <R-bugs@biostat.ku.dk>
To: paul@stat.auckland.ac.nz
Subject: Re: legend() with xpd=T; omission of initial plot character (PR#943)
Date: Tue Jul 17 04:28:44 2001
