	id <m17HwxI-000IXcC@franz.stat.wisc.edu> (Debian Smail3.2.0.114)
	for <r-bugs@r-project.org>; Tue, 11 Jun 2002 20:29:48 -0500 (CDT) 
Received: from stat1.stat.auckland.ac.nz (stat1.stat.auckland.ac.nz [130.216.93.1])
