This looks like a bug?
Unable to use scan(pipe()) while profiling.
I have no idea whether this version of R violates the
    "do not use `Rprof' in an executable built for profiling"
warning in ?Rprof.

Thanks
-Don

>  version
          _
platform powerpc-apple-darwin1.4
arch     powerpc
